title: Micro Photoshop 1.9mb
description:
This is the old version of photoshop(2.5) which takes only 1.9mb but provides all the basic image editing functions. Just double click the EXE file and press Install. The shortcut will be placed on the desktop automatically. No serial or crack requiered. 
You can store and download it online even through dialup. or store it in your mailbox, so that you can use photoshop in any system having an internet connection.
